<!-- FAQ -->
<section class="pricing-faq">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header">
      <div class="tag">FAQ</div>
      <h2>Frequently Asked <span>Questions</span></h2>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-grid">
      <div class="faq-item">
        <h4>How does the subscription work?</h4>
        <p>You subscribe to a monthly plan, submit design requests via our project board, and we deliver within the stated timeframe. Pause or cancel anytime — no contracts.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <h4>What if I need a one-time project?</h4>
        <p>We also accept one-time project commissions with custom quotes. Contact us and describe your project for a tailored proposal.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <h4>How do revisions work?</h4>
        <p>All plans include unlimited revisions. We iterate until you're 100% satisfied. We don't close a request until you approve it.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <h4>Do I own the final designs?</h4>
        <p>Yes — full IP and ownership transfers to you upon delivery. We also provide all source files (Figma, AI, PSD) with every project.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <h4>Can I pause my subscription?</h4>
        <p>Absolutely. If you're going on vacation or need to pause for any reason, you can freeze your billing cycle and resume when ready.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <h4>What design tools do you use?</h4>
        <p>Primarily Figma for UI/UX, Adobe Illustrator for brand/print, After Effects for motion, and Webflow or Framer for web design delivery.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

